      "span_text": "Total RNA from cell cultures was purified by using the RNeasy kit (Qiagen Inc). Ten micrograms of total RNA from HepG2 cells or 2.5 g of total RNA from HeLa Tet On cell lines was subjected to electrophoresis on 1% agarose gel, transferred to Hybond-N membranes (Amersham Pharmacia Biotech), and hybridized with cDNA probes for human PON1, PON3, and GAPDH. Electrophoresis and hybridization protocols have been described previously. [CITATION_1] "
